<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>12705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘爬到皮特的后背上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18572</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们终于安全了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们成功了，皮特！”她大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25647</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的计划真不错。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25648</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘和皮特一刻不停的飞，飞了很久很久。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39456</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果你觉得冷，就藏到我的羽毛下面。”他对拇指姑娘说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39457</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44474</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，你从哪里学来的秘密对话歌曲？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44475</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51215</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我曾经遇见两只鸟，克里斯和麦琪。”拇指姑娘骄傲地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51216</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53298</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是他们教我的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56931</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你学得真好。”皮特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56932</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62308</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你还好吗？”拇指姑娘担心皮特没有了力气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62309</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66688</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能飞的感觉真好。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66689</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没有翅膀。”拇指姑娘说，“但是我在飞！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她朝下看了看，看到了几排房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>房子的屋顶上都盖着雪，有几个孩子在堆雪人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90131</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道要去哪儿了。”皮特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“慢慢飞。”拇指姑娘说，“我想慢慢看这个世界。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们飞过一个湖，拇指姑娘看到水上有什么东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108384</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看到一些鸭子！”她边说边指。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那是好消息，意味着我们就快到了。”皮特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114131</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在感觉空气暖和了很多，下面的景色也变了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127865</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我看到了一些绿树，皮特。”她喊道，“还有花！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127866</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们飞到花园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从上面看那些花，就像一排排彩色的蜡烛!”她喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141519</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要降落了。”皮特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141520</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145571</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在花园里的花朵附近落下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145572</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘看了看四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在他们旁边正好有一些红色的花，但是还没完全开放。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们好美啊。”拇指姑娘说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165466</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她觉得这些花是郁金香，但是不确定。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165467</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169884</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里才是你应该在的地方。”皮特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么意思？”拇指姑娘问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178079</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我第一次见你的时候，”皮特开始说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178080</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就知道你从很远的地方来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，我和玛丽戈尔德夫人住在一起。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194577</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，不是的，你的家在这里。”皮特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194578</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197990</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不明白。”拇指姑娘说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197991</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很快你会明白的。”皮特回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见，拇指姑娘，谢谢你为我做的一切。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206538</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，别走！”拇指姑娘恳求道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，我们会很快再见面的。”皮特说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>拇指姑娘看着她的朋友飞走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见，皮特！”她向皮特喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229900</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然一朵花开始晃动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229901</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是最大的那朵。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后花瓣一片接着一片打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇。”拇指姑娘感叹道，她紧紧盯着花朵里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247076</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谁打扰了我的美梦？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247077</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255293</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人从花里走了出来，他跟拇指姑娘一样大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255294</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。”拇指姑娘结结巴巴地说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260946</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是故意大声喊叫的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人看着拇指姑娘，拇指姑娘也看着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那些是翅膀吗？”她问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人的背后有一对翅膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>